Steps to improve performance of microservices


1. Parallelize the business logic of api if it can be done using threads or futures or async code.
2. Use appropriate data structures if applicable and write optimized code
3. Introduce caching of frequently queried objects.
4. Database optimization (you already know)
5. Rate limiting and throttling 
6. Horizontal scale and vertical scaling 
7. CDN and load balancers


